{"ProductId":"370","Title":"VertiStack® Avante®","ShortDescription":"Unique, compact design stacks sections on the wall above the opening, eliminating the need for overhead tracks, exposed hinges, track or cable.","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/vertistack-showcase.webp?sfvrsn=fd33839_11","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/vertistack-avante","Overview":"<h3>Built for Modern Living</h3><h4>Commercial-Grade Strength</h4><p>The VertiStack&reg; Avante&reg; features a rugged 2-5/8\" aluminum frame built to handle daily use while keeping maintenance to a minimum.</p><h4>Design Options</h4><p>Personalize your door with a wide range of finishes&mdash;including anodized, painted, or powder-coated aluminum&mdash;and choose from glass, acrylic, polycarbonate, or solid aluminum panels.</p><h4>Light and Insulation, Your Way</h4><p><a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg; polyurethane insulation</a> in the stiles and rails (R-value 3.8) helps keep your space comfortable, while optional tempered insulated glass adds another layer of efficiency.</p><h4>Built for Any Climate</h4><p><a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg; reinforcement</a> is available for those who need extra protection in high-wind areas.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li><li>Meets ASHRAE&reg; 90.1 Title 24 and IECC&reg; (International Energy Conservation Code) 2021 Section C406.9 Air Infiltration requirements.</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>Engineered for Strength and Seamless Space</h3><p>The VertiStack&reg; Avante&reg; is built with a tough, 2-5/8\" commercial-grade aluminum frame that stands up to everyday wear and tear. The frame resists rust and corrosion, making it a <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/how-to-choose-the-right-garage-door-for-your-climate\">smart pick for any climate</a>. Each section is filled with Intellicore&reg; polyurethane insulation, so you get better temperature control and a quieter garage (R-value 3.8). Choose from a variety of panel options&mdash;tempered glass, acrylic, polycarbonate, or solid aluminum&mdash;to match your style and needs.</p><p>One of the standout features is the open-concept stacking design. Instead of swinging overhead, the door sections stack tightly along the wall with minimal projection, leaving your ceiling clear for lights, storage, or even tall vehicles. The panels can even disappear into a recessed soffit, keeping your garage open and uncluttered. Safety brackets and sturdy hardware round out the package for peace of mind and long-lasting performance.</p>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"VertiStack Avante","DisplayIndex":10,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/vertistack-avante","ColorDisclaimer":"<p>The VertiStack&reg; Avante&reg; offers a range of finishes designed to complement any modern home. Choose from classic Clear Aluminum (anodized) for a clean, contemporary vibe, or opt for Standard White for a crisp, timeless look. If you&rsquo;re after a touch of warmth or drama, painted finishes like Bronze or Chocolate add rich, understated color that stands out without overpowering your exterior.</p><p>You can also choose from our dramatic anodized options include Bronze, Black, and Dark Bronze. Each one creates a striking, architectural feel and highlights the door&rsquo;s streamlined aluminum design. But no matter which you choose, every finish is engineered for durability and long-lasting beauty.</p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"","HardwareDisclaimer":"","DesignDisclaimer":"","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Avante<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> – Now Available with C-Power™ Technology","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/tnahcpower01showcase.webp?sfvrsn=e1a1ed6c_1","Id":"16","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/avante","DisplayIndex":9,"ShortDescription":"Aluminum and glass doors that make your garage a stunning focal point, providing natural light by day and a dramatic glow at night","AlternativeText":"Avante"},{"Title":"Avante<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Sleek – Now Available with C-Power™ Technology","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/avante-az-595.webp?sfvrsn=70ef6b44_10","Id":"290","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/avantesleek","DisplayIndex":10,"ShortDescription":"Minimalist frames and slim horizontal windows for bright, unobstructed views","AlternativeText":"Avante Sleek"}],"ProductBrochures":[{"Title":"VertiStack Avante Brochure","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/rsdr-vertistackss-24.webp?sfvrsn=912040da_3","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-VERTISTACKSS-24.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1},{"Title":"Products Available Through Independent Dealers","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/idea-book.webp?sfvrsn=699cfb64_5","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-IMAGINE-14.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":2}],"ProductInstallationAndCare":[{"Title":"VertiStack Avante Care and Maintenance Manual","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/vertistack-avante-care.webp?sfvrsn=f10de895_1","Type":"Finish & Care","Url":"https://literature.clopay.co